{"tid":458733,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【10 月新番】 三月的獅子 二期 集中討論","createTime":"2017-11-05T07:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T17:18:03.000Z","uid":129230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b237837a0b76df58a0a7198aaaa4da7365dbafd3","tid":458733,"uid":129230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ll0yQlgF_I8/WakpaCnpAyI/AAAAAAAADdc/qijb6YZi1wQWi-UBRdwjH-Z6dSMdCyFPwCLcBGAs/s1600/0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ll0yQlgF_I8%2FWakpaCnpAyI%2FAAAAAAAADdc%2Fqijb6YZi1wQWi-UBRdwjH-Z6dSMdCyFPwCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F0.png&h=9be4a421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《3月的獅子》（日語：3月のライオン）是羽海野千花的漫畫作品。2007年於白泉社《Young Animal》連載。原則上是每號連載，由於休載較多一些實質上是不定期連載。題材為將棋，所以擔任監修一職的人物是先崎學棋士九段。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">原作:\t羽海野千花<br />\n導演:\t新房昭之<br />\n人物設定:\t杉山延寛<br />\n音樂:\t橋本由香利<br />\n動畫製作:\tSHAFT</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">桐山零：河西健吾<br />\n川本あかり：茅野愛衣<br />\n川本ひなた：花澤香菜<br />\n川本モモ：久野美咲<br />\n二海堂晴信：岡本信彦<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇完最新一集 見到日向真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n點解三月的獅子會冇PO.... 忍唔住開左個  今季最中意睇 見到男主開始發力"},{"pid":"1e52f7460226c2f0b4e69ed683d582aec969b63f","tid":458733,"uid":129230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T07:21:37.000Z","msg":"大家可以唔洗再理E個PO 原來有人開左 SORRY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明我搜尋個陣搵唔到.."},{"pid":"f69e4befb006e5df813293ca976af8d651b34f37","tid":458733,"uid":117042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家可以唔洗再理E個PO 原來有人開左 SORRY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明我搜尋個陣搵唔到..</blockquote><br />\nE+又得呢個係第二期post<br />\n第四集真係難忘，個訓導金句等左好耐"}]}